From mlee Malcolm Lee Subject Re A KIND and LOVING God In article writes Leviticus And the daughter of any priest if she profane herself by playing the whore she profaneth her father she shall be burnt with Deuteronomy the tokens of virginity be not found for the damsel then they shall bring out the damsel to the door of her father's house and the men of the city shall stone her with stones that she Deuteronomy If a man be found lying with a woman married to a husband then they shall both of them Deuteronomy If a damsel that is a virgin be betrothed unto a husband and a man find her in the city and lie with her then ye shall bring them both out unto the gate of that city and ye shall stone them with stones that they Deuteronomy BUT if a man find a betrothed damsel in the field and the man force her and lie with her then the man only that lay with her shall These laws written for the Israelites God's chosen people whom God had expressly set apart from the rest of the The Israelites were a direct witness to God's To disobey God after KNOWing that God is real would be an outright denial of God and therefore immediately Remember these laws were written for a different time and applied only to God's chosen But Jesus has changed all of We are living in the age of Sin is no longer immediately punishable by There is repentance and there is salvation through our Lord Jesus And not just for a few chosen Salvation is available to everyone Jew and Gentile God be with you Malcolm Lee